title: The One Where Lala Gets Hit In The Face By A Golf Club
description:
Golf club swings gone awry, seat belt trauma, and “Spy Kids” on the TV/VCR combo in the car! Those are just a few stories from Lala, her mom Lisa, and her brother Easton. Who was the easier baby? Who went through a hiding phase? What was the best family vacation, and what traditions and crazy stories do they hope to continue with Ocean? It’s a hilariously sweet episode with Lala’s family!
